text: Pine Iosefa is an I-Kiribati football coach. In 2011 Pine Iosefa was chief coach of the Kiribati national football team for the Football at the 2011 Pacific Games. ==External links== * Soccerway Category:I-Kiribati football managers Category:Living people Category:Kiribati national football team managers Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
